---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Gym & Fitness Center Marketing Automation"
  description="Gym and fitness center marketing automation in Canada. Convert trial visitors into paying members and reduce churn with smart follow-up."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-red-900 to-slate-900 text-white py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><circle cx=%2250%22 cy=%2250%22 r=%221%22 fill=%22white%22/></svg>'); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <a href="/industries" class="inline-flex items-center text-red-300 hover:text-red-200 mb-6 transition">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          All Industries
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Marketing Automation for
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-400">Gyms & Fitness Centers</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Convert trial members, reduce cancellations, and build a community that keeps members engaged for years.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/book-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:from-red-600 hover:to-orange-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-red-500/30">
            Book Your Free Discovery Call
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-slate-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>ROI Calculator</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white border-b">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">67%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Trial-to-member conversion</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">34%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Reduced cancellations</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">89%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Reactivation rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">2.3x</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Referral increase</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Gym Industry Challenge
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
          Most gyms lose members faster than they gain them. Without engagement systems, January signups become February cancellations.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">High Churn Rate</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Members sign up motivated but stop coming. Cancellations pile up.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Trial No-Shows</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Free trial signups never actually show up. Wasted leads and marketing dollars.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Silent Cancellations</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Members cancel without warning. No chance to save them or understand why.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Low Engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Members don't feel connected. They're just paying for access, not community.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Missed Upsells</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Personal training, classes, supplements—upsell opportunities slip away.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Weak Referrals</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Happy members don't bring friends. No referral program drives word-of-mouth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          How We Help Gyms Grow Membership
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
          Convert trials, reduce churn, and build an engaged community that refers friends and stays for years.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trial Conversion Sequences</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated sequences that confirm trials, drive show-ups, and convert visitors to members.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Trial confirmations</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Show-up reminders</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Post-visit follow-up</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Member Engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Onboarding sequences, workout tips, and milestone celebrations that keep members coming back.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>New member onboarding</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Visit streak rewards</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Fitness tips & content</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-lime-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-yellow-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Churn Prevention</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">At-risk detection based on visit frequency drops with save campaigns before they cancel.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>At-risk detection</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Win-back campaigns</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Freeze/pause options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Referral Programs</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated referral campaigns that turn happy members into your best marketing channel.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Member referral links</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Dual rewards</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Referral tracking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-red-400 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "Our trial-to-member conversion jumped to 67%. Cancellations dropped 34% because we catch at-risk members early. Member referrals increased 2.3x. Best investment we've made."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              JR
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Jordan Rodriguez</div>
              <div class="text-slate-600">Owner, Peak Fitness • Mississauga, ON</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- FAQ & Demo CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-accent-100 dark:bg-accent-900/30 rounded-full mb-6">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-300">Interactive Demo</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        See What Your Website Could Look Like
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Enter your business name, phone number, colors, and services , and watch a personalized website preview come to life in seconds.
      </p>
      <a href="/demos/fitness" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg">
        Build Your Free Demo
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">100% free. No signup required. Takes 30 seconds</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ready to Grow Your Gym?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-red-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Book a free demo and see exactly how we'll increase conversions and reduce churn.
      </p>
      <a href="/book-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition shadow-lg">
        Book Your Free Discovery Call
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mt-4 md:mt-0 md:ml-4 border-2 border-white/50 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
        Calculate ROI
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

